page.title: 25Liverpool Central North 2011
page.content:
The frontage of the River Mersey is no longer deserted. The regeneration of the Dock area has spread from the Albert Dock and has seen an influx of leisure outlets including hotels, offices, an arena and many shops servicing the many residential area's that have sprung up along the banks of the river, from the city centre towards Aigburth.
Contribution by: Miss Maria Jones
